---
import GuideLayout from '../layouts/GuideLayout.astro';
---

<GuideLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - UK Salary and Tax Calculator Website"
  description="Our privacy policy explains how we handle your data. No cookies, no tracking and no salary data stored. All tax calculations run entirely in your browser."
  slug="/privacy"
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>

  <h2>What data we collect</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Short answer: almost nothing.</strong> All calculator inputs are processed
    entirely in your browser. We never see, store, or transmit your salary figures.
  </p>

  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>
    We use <a href="https://plausible.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plausible Analytics</a>,
    a privacy-friendly analytics tool. Plausible does not use cookies, does not collect
    personal data, and is fully compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR. This means
    <strong>no cookie banner is needed</strong>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Plausible collects only aggregate, anonymous data: page views, referral sources,
    browser type, and country. No individual visitors can be identified.
  </p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    We do not set any cookies. No first-party cookies, no third-party cookies,
    no tracking cookies.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>
    This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect minimal technical
    data (IP address, request headers) as part of their CDN service. See
    <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    Google Fonts are loaded for typography. Google may collect standard web request
    data. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's privacy policy</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>
    We may display ads via Google AdSense in the future. If enabled, Google's ad
    personalisation and cookie policies will apply. We will update this page
    before activating any advertising.
  </p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    Since we don't collect personal data, there is nothing to request, correct,
    or delete. If you have any privacy-related questions, contact us at
    <strong>hello@realsalary.co.uk</strong>.
  </p>
</GuideLayout>
